      <title>算法分析——分治策略</title>
      <link href="/archives/be82d226.html"/>
      <url>/archives/be82d226.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-分治策略的基本思想"><a href="#1-分治策略的基本思想" class="headerlink" title="1.分治策略的基本思想"></a>1.分治策略的基本思想</h1><ol><li>将原始问题划分，使其归结为规模较小的子问题</li><li>递归或迭代求解每个子问题</li><li>将子问题的解综合得到原问题的解</li></ol><p><font color=red>注意：</font></p><ol><li>子问题与原始问题性质完全一样</li><li>子问题之间可彼此独立求解</li><li>递归停止时子问题可直接求解</li></ol><h1 id="2-分治算法的引入"><a href="#2-分治算法的引入" class="headerlink" title="2.分治算法的引入"></a>2.分治算法的引入</h1><h2 id="2-1-二分检索"><a href="#2-1-二分检索" class="headerlink" title="2.1.二分检索"></a>2.1.二分检索</h2><h3 id="2-1-1-二分检索的代码实现"><a href="#2-1-1-二分检索的代码实现" class="headerlink" title="2.1.1.二分检索的代码实现"></a>2.1.1.二分检索的代码实现</h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">Binary_Search</span><span class="params">(SeqList L,ElemType key)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> low = <span class="number">0</span>,high = L.TableLen - <span class="number">1</span>,mid;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(low &lt;= high)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        mid = (low + high)/<span class="number">2</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(L.elem[mid]==key)</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> mid;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span>(L.elem[mid]&gt;key)</span><br><span class="line">            high = mid - <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span> low = mid + <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">-1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>通过和中间元素的比较，不断将问题归结为规模减半的子问题。</p><h3 id="2-1-2-二分检索的时间复杂度分析"><a href="#2-1-2-二分检索的时间复杂度分析" class="headerlink" title="2.1.2.二分检索的时间复杂度分析"></a>2.1.2.二分检索的时间复杂度分析</h3><p>递推方程：<em>W(n) = w(n/2) + 1</em></p><p>​                  <em>W(1) = 1</em></p><p>解得 <em>W(n) = logn + 1</em></p>]]></content>
      
      
